<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Beside services and models, you may want to store your own mappers in your modules as well. Thus the module resource autoloader should also have a "mappers" =&gt; "Mapper" directive in its standard definition.</p>

<p>As we currently have Model_DbTable mapped to models/DbTable we would probably either want to map Model_Mapper to models/Mapper, as Ralph would agree, but I still think that mappers belong to their own directory in the modules' root.</p>

<p>This topic needs further discussion.</p>

